---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---
<Base
  title="Uses · Gabriel Rubens"
  description="The tools I use every day to build and ship."
>
  <div class="page-eyebrow">// uses</div>
  <h1 class="page-title">What I <em>use</em>.</h1>
  <p class="page-lede">
    A short, honest list of the tools I actually reach for. Nothing here is
    sponsored. This page exists because I find other people's <code>/uses</code>
    pages genuinely useful, so here's mine.
  </p>

  <div class="uses-grid">
    <div class="uses-card">
      <h3>Hardware<em>.</em></h3>
      <ul>
        <li><b>MacBook</b><span class="note">daily driver</span></li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="uses-card">
      <h3>Editor <em>&amp; tools</em></h3>
      <ul>
        <li><b>VS Code</b><span class="note">daily</span></li>
        <li><b>Claude Code</b><span class="note">pair</span></li>
        <li><b>Xcode</b><span class="note">ios builds</span></li>
        <li><b>Android Studio</b><span class="note">android builds</span></li>
        <li><b>iTerm2 + tmux</b><span class="note">terminal</span></li>
        <li><b>Figma</b><span class="note">design</span></li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="uses-card">
      <h3>Stack<em>.</em></h3>
      <ul>
        <li><b>Rails 8 + Ruby 3.4</b><span class="note">backend</span></li>
        <li><b>Hotwire</b><span class="note">turbo + stimulus</span></li>
        <li><b>Hotwire Native</b><span class="note">ios + android</span></li>
        <li><b>Django</b><span class="note">pensio only</span></li>
        <li><b>PostgreSQL</b><span class="note">data</span></li>
        <li><b>Kamal 2</b><span class="note">deploys</span></li>
        <li><b>Hostinger VPS</b><span class="note">hosting</span></li>
        <li><b>Cloudflare</b><span class="note">dns + cdn</span></li>
        <li><b>Stripe + RevenueCat</b><span class="note">payments</span></li>
        <li><b>Blueprint</b><span class="note">my own template</span></li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="uses-card">
      <h3>Fuel<em>.</em></h3>
      <ul>
        <li><b>Filtered coffee</b><span class="note">mornings</span></li>
        <li><b>Noise-cancelling headphones</b><span class="note">focus</span></li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>
</Base>
